<section id="newsletter" class="scroll-mt-24 bg-brand-900 py-14">
	<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center justify-between gap-8 px-4 sm:flex-row sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="max-w-xl text-center sm:text-left">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl">Receba comparativos por e-mail</h2>
			<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
				Sem spam; você cancela quando quiser. (No site ao vivo, o dono do site liga este formulário ao serviço de e-mail dele.)
			</p>
		</div>
		<form class="flex w-full max-w-md flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center" action="#" method="post">
			<label class="sr-only" for="newsletter-email">E-mail</label>
			<input
				id="newsletter-email"
				type="email"
				name="email"
				required
				placeholder="seu@email.com"
				class="w-full rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-5 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder:text-white/45 outline-none ring-2 ring-transparent focus:border-white/40 focus:ring-white/20"
			/>
			<button
				type="submit"
				class="shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-900 transition hover:bg-white/90"
			>
				Inscrever
			</button>
		</form>
	</div>
</section>
